               <p>559. 
               <persName id="t17970920-76-defend570" type="defendantName">
                  JOSEPH 
                  COURT
               <interp inst="t17970920-76-defend570" type="surname" value="COURT"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17970920-76-defend570" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17970920-76-defend570" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was indicted for <rs id="t17970920-76-off401" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17970920-76-off401" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17970920-76-off401" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17970920-76-cd402" type="crimeDate">9th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970920-76-off401 t17970920-76-cd402"></join>, eight pair of gold ear-rings, value 3l. 16s. one hundred and twenty-one pair of other gold ear-rings, value 74l. 10s. 6d. forty-eight other pair of gold earrings, value 12l. 12s. two hundred and four pair<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179709200081"></xptr>of other gold ear-rings, value 361. 9s twenty-four other pair of gold ear-ings set with paste, value 61.6s. two thousand four hundred and eighty-eight gold beads value 721. 18S eight hundred and sixty-four gold coloured beads, value, 81. one hundred and forty-four pair of other gold ear-ings, value 201.8S three pair of gold enamelled bracelets, value 91. three shall cases for bracelets, value 6s. six gold medallions, value 9l. thirty-six gold seals, value 331.12s. twelve eggraved gold neck lockets, value 31. and a parcel of leather shoes, value 14s. 8d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17970920-76-victim572" type="victimName">
                           John Alexander 
                           Mackenzie
                        <interp inst="t17970920-76-victim572" type="surname" value="Mackenzie"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17970920-76-victim572" type="given" value="John Alexander"></interp>
